'''2010年3月3日巴古拜爆炸事件'''是2010年3月3日发生在[[伊拉克|伊拉克]][[巴古拜|巴古拜]]的3颗炸弹连环爆炸事件，目前为止已造成至少33人死亡，55人受伤。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/03/04/world/middleeast/04iraq.html|title=Bombers Kill Dozens as Iraq Vote Nears|last=Santora|first=Mark|date=3 March 2010|work=The New York Times|accessdate=4 March 2010|location=New York, NY|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109040721/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/03/04/world/middleeast/04iraq.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2010/03/201033961873832.html|title=Suicide bombers target Iraq city|date=3 March 2010|publisher=Al-Jazeera|accessdate=4 March 2010|archive-date=2010-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100304030427/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2010/03/201033961873832.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>巴古拜是一座[[什叶派|什叶派]]和[[逊尼派|逊尼派]]共同居住的[[城市|城市]]，是[[迪亚拉省|迪亚拉省]]的[[首府|首府]]，离[[巴格达|巴格达]]大约40[[英里|英里]]（64千米）。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/ca52f004-26c8-11df-bd0c-00144feabdc0.html|title=Suicide bomb attacks kill 30 in Iraq|last=England|first=Andrew|date=3 March 2010|work=The Financial Times|accessdate=4 March 2010|archive-date=2010-03-04|archive-url=https://archive.is/20100304051101/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/ca52f004-26c8-11df-bd0c-00144feabdc0.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

爆炸发生在2010年3月7日将举行的[[2010年伊拉克议会选举|议会选举]]的筹备阶段。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.latimes.com/news/nation-and-world/la-fg-iraq-bombing4-2010mar04,0,7848363.story|title=Iraq suicide bombings kill 31 as elections near|last=Sly|first=Liz|coauthors=Redha, Usama|date=3 March 2010|work=The Los Angeles Times|accessdate=4 March 2010|location=Los Angeles, CA|archive-date=2010-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100304214348/http://www.latimes.com/news/nation-and-world/la-fg-iraq-bombing4-2010mar04,0,7848363.story|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.globalconflictmaps.com/2010/03/03/suicide-bombings-in-baqubah-iraq-kill-31/?utm_source=twitterfeed&utm_medium=twitter|title=Suicide Bombings in Baqubah, Iraq Kill 32 (video)|last=|first=|coauthors=|date=3 March 2010|work=Associated Press|accessdate=4 March 2010|location=|archive-date=2016-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314121053/http://www.globalconflictmaps.com/2010/03/03/suicide-bombings-in-baqubah-iraq-kill-31/?utm_medium=twitter&utm_source=twitterfeed|dead-url=no}}</ref>当地时间上午9:45，第一枚[[汽车炸弹|汽车炸弹]]在该城西区的一[[警察局|警察局]]门口被引爆；过了一会儿，距离第一次爆炸现场约100码（91[[米_(單位)|米]]）<ref name="WSJ">{{cite news|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748704541304575099592811311992.html?mod=WSJ_hpp_sections_world|title=Suicide Bombs Rock Iraq Before Vote|last=Levinson|first=Charles|date=4 March 2010|work=The Wall Street Journal|publisher=Dow Jones & Company|accessdate=4 March 2010|archive-date=2010-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100305111024/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748704541304575099592811311992.html?mod=WSJ_hpp_sections_world|dead-url=no}}</ref>的迪亚拉省政府大楼装置好的一枚汽车炸弹也被引爆<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2010/03/03/AR2010030300644.html?hpid=topnews|title=Pre-election bombings kill dozens in Iraqi city|last=Londoño|first=Ernesto|date=3 March 2010|work=The Washington Post|accessdate=4 March 2010|location=Washington, DC|archive-date=2016-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130152439/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2010/03/03/AR2010030300644.html?hpid=topnews|dead-url=no}}</ref>；后来，一名自杀式袭击者在一[[医院|医院]]引爆[[炸弹|炸弹]]，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/iraq/article7048804.ece|title=Suicide attacks kill at least 32 in Baquba|last=August|first=Oliver|date=4 March 2010|work=The Times|accessdate=4 March 2010|location=London, UK|archive-date=2011-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110605005907/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/iraq/article7048804.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>并炸伤一名[[警察|警察]]，被救护车送往另一医院接受治疗。<ref name="WSJ" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5hwK_CSpBxsNuVUEaDuOwmSSCiqGwD9E7BD4G2|title=Triple bombing kill 32 ahead of Iraqi vote|last=Hubbard|first=Ben|date=3 March 2010|publisher=The Associated Press|accessdate=4 March 2010|archive-date=2010-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100308030744/http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5hwK_CSpBxsNuVUEaDuOwmSSCiqGwD9E7BD4G2|dead-url=no}}</ref>第四枚炸弹在医院附近被发现并及时拆除。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/iraq/7361744/Iraq-hit-by-triple-suicide-bomb-ahead-of-election.html|title=Iraq hit by triple suicide bomb ahead of election|last=Spencer|first=Richard|date=3 March 2010|work=The Telegraph|accessdate=4 March 2010|location=London, UK|archive-date=2016-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130152439/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/iraq/7361744/Iraq-hit-by-triple-suicide-bomb-ahead-of-election.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

爆炸发生后，巴古拜市进行了全面宵禁，甚至禁止行人上街。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.miamiherald.com/2010/03/03/1510517/at-least-33-iraqis-die-in-3-pre.html|title=At least 33 Iraqis die in 3 pre-election bombings|last=Allam|first=Hannah|date=3 March 2010|work=Miami Herald|publisher=McClatchy Newspapers|accessdate=4 March 2010|archive-date=2019-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822040803/https://www.miamiherald.com/2010/03/03/1510517/at-least-33-iraqis-die-in-3-pre.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>爆炸中的死者包括10名警察<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/world/2010/0304/1224265559279.html|title=10 policemen among 33 killed in Iraq suicide attacks|last=Jansen|first=Michael|date=4 March 2010|work=The Irish Times|accessdate=4 March 2010|location=Dublin|archive-date=2012-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020094242/http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/world/2010/0304/1224265559279.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>和迪亚拉省卫生部门负责人阿里·提米米。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/world/2010-03/03/content_9533016.htm|title=30 killed in Diyala triple bombings|date=3 March 2010|work=China Daily|accessdate=4 March 2010|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070722/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/world/2010-03/03/content_9533016.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

爆炸肇事者尚未查明，但[[伊拉克基地组织|伊拉克基地组织]]之前承诺要破坏在3月7日举行的选举。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/8547906.stm|title=Q&A: Iraqi parliamentary polls|date=3 March 2010|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=4 March 2010|archive-date=2010-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100304040522/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/8547906.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>尽管如此，选举的早期投票已按计划在3月4日上午已经举行。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/03/05/world/middleeast/05iraq.html|title=Following Suicide Attacks, Early Voting Begins in Iraq|last=Santora|first=Marc|date=4 March 2010|work=The New York Times|accessdate=4 March 2010|archive-date=2010-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100309035359/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/03/05/world/middleeast/05iraq.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

